{"tid":1244682,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"窮則變，變則通","createTime":"2019-06-20T04:32:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T08:17:55.000Z","uid":62776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7014388afa4f1282a2a378415e38049c87f20a7b","tid":1244682,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:32:06.000Z","msg":"咁多位連登仔<br />\n相信大家呢期無力感都好重下<br />\n<br />\n一則開始冇左個重心目標(雖然冇撤，但佢係依家停左我地就做唔到野)<br />\n<br />\n二則愈爆愈多政府既體制腐敗，仲要官員之間互相傳波A字膊<br />\n<br />\n相信大家都有種技窮既感覺<br />\n但好似我個標題所講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">窮則變 變則通</span></span><br />\n<br />\n到左呢個時候<br />\n大家係時候要再轉變<br />\n諗下我地一直以黎係點做<br />\n由一直用開既遊行，到佔中，到跟住魚革再到69，612<br />\n我地對抗既模式都一直係度進化/改變緊<br />\n好似文宣組出信，廢除膠官外國護照，長輩圖，不合作運動<br />\n有d仲有意想不到既效果<br />\n依家既然覺得野餐再冇用既時候<br />\n大家不妨將個問題由惡法<br />\n轉去黑警度先<br />\n佢地個問題一樣好嚴重<br />\n612 中信<br />\n未能出示委任證<br />\n冇pcid<br />\n病人私隱咁<br />\n呢d全部都係大問題<br />\n既然係咁<br />\n大家應該合力令到個獨立調查委員會成立先<br />\n等班黑警唔可以再事無忌旦咁<br />\n對前線義士用武"},{"pid":"7128aed7f18fdc182383df67570090dad04ca360","tid":1244682,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:01:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f612da0754912e514707c48e3d7422bec9f3ddc","tid":1244682,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:02:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpresident-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbOSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=12a874ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation</a><br />\n<br />\n白宮聯署 解放香港 你簽左未"},{"pid":"a1dafe276bc24ef5821fa5046e2507887cb23643","tid":1244682,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy"